then he took some red thread,

827
01:06:17,099 --> 01:06:20,769
and tied a big horn on top of his head.

828
01:06:24,189 --> 01:06:25,357
All right.

829
01:06:25,899 --> 01:06:27,984
You're a reindeer. Here's your motivation.

830
01:06:28,944 --> 01:06:32,030
