And the Grinch
grabbed the tree, and he started to shove,

891
01:11:45,385 --> 01:11:48,972
when he heard a small sound
like the coo of a dove.

892
01:11:49,180 --> 01:11:50,223
Excuse me.

893
01:11:56,521 --> 01:11:59,858
The Grinch had been caught
by this tiny Who daughter,

894
01:11:59,899 --> 01:12:02,569
who'd got out of bed for a cup of cold water.

895
01:12:02,610 --> 01:12:06,197
Santa Claus?
What are you doing with our tree?

896
01:12:06,573 --> 01:12:10,410
But, you know, that old Grinch
was so smart and so slick,

897
