902
01:12:29,054 --> 01:12:33,099
So I'm taking it home
to my workshop, my dear.

903
01:12:38,229 --> 01:12:40,273
I'll fix it up there,

904
01:12:40,815 --> 01:12:43,902
and I'll bring it back here.

905
01:12:46,279 --> 01:12:48,114
Santa, what's Christmas really about?

906
01:12:48,364 --> 01:12:49,824
Vengeance!

907
01:12:52,077 --> 01:12:53,286
I mean,

908
01:12:55,914 --> 01:12:57,248
