01:18:48,850 --> 01:18:51,477
What an embarrassment! I've been robbed!

958
01:19:21,507 --> 01:19:23,843
Mayor May Who? Oh, dear.

959
01:19:30,850 --> 01:19:34,437
Well, I wonder
who could've done this.

960
01:19:36,189 --> 01:19:37,690
Tell you people one thing.

961
01:19:38,357 --> 01:19:39,859
Invite the Grinch,

962
