01:20:46,425 --> 01:20:48,928
No, no, no, no, not wrecked,
pulverized Christmas.

979
01:20:49,011 --> 01:20:50,763
Is that what I'm hearing from you, Lou?

980
01:20:51,764 --> 01:20:53,933
You can't hurt Christmas, Mr. Mayor,

981
01:20:54,016 --> 01:20:58,187
because it isn't about the gifts
or the contests or the fancy lights.

982
01:20:58,271 --> 01:21:01,440
That's what Cindy's
been trying to tell everyone.

983
01:21:01,941 --> 01:21:04,235
And me. She's been trying to tell me.

984
01:21:04,277 --> 01:21:07,655
What is wrong with you? This is a child.

985
01:21:08,614 --> 01:21:10,157
She's my child.

986
01:21:10,241 --> 01:21:12,785
And she happens to be right, by the way.

987
01:21:21,711 --> 01:21:26,007
I don't need anything more
for Christmas than this right here, my family.

988
