997
01:22:19,518 --> 01:22:22,396
The crescendo of my odious opus!

998
01:22:22,855 --> 01:22:24,357
Yes!

999
01:22:28,194 --> 01:22:31,405
Oh, the wailing and the gnashing of teeth.

1000
